-----------

EaselJS example that shows how to create persistent designs using stage.autoClear as false.

Also, shows how to subclass DisplayObjects in order to have them move and draw themselves, which can 
dramatically simplify code.

Also includes some code that shows how to save and restore canvas graphics when it is resized.